nodes.text: "Return to Endor" is an article by Rich Handley that appeared in Star Wars Insider 62. It features interviews and information about the cast of the Ewok films, Caravan of Courage: An Ewok Adventure and Ewoks: The Battle for Endor. Actors profiled are Warwick Davis, Eric Walker, Aubree Miller, Fionnula Flanagan, Guy Boyd, Paul Gleason, Carel Struycken, and Siân Phillips.
